    <div class="row">

    <p>Self talk is our inner voice, our conversation we think and hear in our mind. It can be either positive or negative. Self talk can control the way you feel about yourself and your thought process. Positive self talk can help you make friends, build self-esteem, boost your confidence, and feel in control. Negative self talk can make you feel down about yourself, depressed, or inferior compared to others. When negative self talk occurs it can be a weight on you and increase your amount of stress.</p>

    <p class="toBold">Examples of Self-Talk</p>
